        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Coralliozetus clausus. A) Holotype (USNM 451460), 13.2 mm SL male after preservation; B) Right side of head of paratype (USNM 451461), 13.5 mm SL male showing dots on operculum; C) Left side of head of same specimen as B) showing dots on branchiostegal rays; D) 12.7 mm SL female (USNM 451461); E) Photo of freshly caught male specimen from Isla del Coco." ;
